p: The model fitted closely to the acceptable ranges from the empirical data for all 51 outputs. Figure 1 shows model fits in a range of years to HIV prevalence, ART coverage, the proportion of people starting ART with CD4 < 250 cells/μl, and the proportion of people starting ART who are female; male partnership incidence in 2015; male and female ART dropout and restart rates; and 12-month retention on ART. Model fits to an additional 28 outputs are given in McCreesh et al. [ 10].
